result.notes:
Abundance and biomass of each log <sup>...</sup> weight class for each 
species in each sample, standardised to area of seabed sampled. Includes 
sample locations, sampling gear used, biological and behavioural trait 
information for each taxon, measured environmental variables for water column 
and sediment, remote sensed chlorophyll and fishing effort data (Vessel 
Monitoring Systems, VMS) for each location.
